Package xxl.binarySearchTrees

This package provides binary search trees like AVL- and red-black-trees.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AVLTree A binary tree where the absolute difference between the height of the subtrees of a Node is limited by 1.
BBTree A binary tree where the balance of every subtree is bounded.
BinarySearchTree BinarySearchTree is a generic implementation of the funcionality of binary search trees.
RedBlackTree A binary tree that is equivalent to a 2-3-tree.
 

Package xxl.binarySearchTrees Description

This package provides binary search trees like AVL- and red-black-trees. It provides a generic binary search tree implementation that is used to implement avl trees and red black trees.
Author: Jochen van den Bercken
